  <body id="s">
    <p>Associate with the polar head groups of membranes<br>
      Relatively loosely associated with membrane<br>
      through ionic interactions with the lipids or aqueous domains of integral
      membrane proteins<br>
      Removed by disrupting ionic interactions either with high salt or change
      in pH<br>
      Purified peripheral membrane proteins are no longer associated with any
      lipids</p>
